00049 typedef struct bActionActuator {                                
00050     struct bAction *act;    /* Pointer to action */             
00051     short   type, flag;     /* Playback type */  // not in use
00052     float   sta, end;       /* Start & End frames */            
00053     char    name[64];       /* For property-driven playback, MAX_NAME */    
00054     char    frameProp[64];  /* Set this property to the actions current frame, MAX_NAME */
00055     short   blendin;        /* Number of frames of blending */
00056     short   priority;       /* Execution priority */
00057     short   layer;          /* Animation layer */
00058     short   end_reset;  /* Ending the actuator (negative pulse) wont reset the the action to its starting frame */
00059     short   strideaxis;     /* Displacement axis */
00060     short   pad;
00061     float   stridelength;   /* Displacement incurred by cycle */ // not in use
00062     float   layer_weight;   /* How much of the previous layer to use for blending. (<0 = disable, 0 = add mode) */
00063 } bActionActuator;
